trans-unit.source: Collects exceptions that occurred during XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: Coleta as exceções que ocorreram durante a descoberta de serviços Web em XML.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Errors%2A> property of <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> is of type <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol.Errors%2A> propriedade <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryClientProtocol> é do tipo <xref:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL that caused an exception during XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: A URL que causou uma exceção durante a descoberta de serviços Web em XML.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> that occurred during XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> que ocorreu durante a descoberta de serviços Web em XML.

trans-unit.source: Adds an <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> with a key of <paramref name="url" /> to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona uma <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> com uma chave de <paramref name="url" /> à <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: An entry with a key of <paramref name="url" /> already exists in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma entrada com uma chave <paramref name="url" /> já existe no <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> to locate within the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: A URL da <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> a ser localizada no <see cref="T:System.Exception" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> contains an <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> with the specified URL.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> atual contém um <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> com a URL especificada.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> contains an <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> with the specified URL; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" /> contém uma <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> com a URL especificada; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the discovery document that caused an exception to be thrown during XML Web services discovery.
trans-unit.target: A URL do documento de descoberta que causou a geração de uma exceção durante a descoberta de serviços Web em XML.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> that occurred while discovering the specified URL from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> que ocorreu ao descobrir a URL especificada do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> that was thrown discovering <paramref name="url" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> que foi lançada descobrindo <paramref name="url" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> object with all the keys in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> com todas as chaves na <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> containing the keys of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> que contém as chaves do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: The URL of the <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> to remove from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: A URL da <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> a remover do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: Removes an <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> with the specified URL from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Remove uma <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> com a URL especificada do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="url" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="url" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> object containing all the values in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> que contém todos os valores no <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> containing the values in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> que contém os valores de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Discovery.DiscoveryExceptionDictionary" />.
